doc.title: Ukubuka konke kwelinki evulekileko ngesandiso
doc.description:
Isengezo lesi sikuvumela bona ulawule lula bona ama-hyperlink avulwa njani.

Iwindi: amanye amabhrawuza, amafasitela avela phezulu, amafasitela amatjha, amafasitela amatjha we-incognito, ifasitela lamanje (okuzenzakalelayo)

Amathebhu: ngesinceleni sethebhu yamanje, ithebhu yamanje, ngesidleni sethebhu yamanje (okuzenzakalelayo)

Isimo sokusebenza: asisebenzi, vula masinyane (okuzenzakalelayo)
